1-Create a twitter account.
2-Log in with your Twitter user account at https://apps.Twitter.com/
3-Click on developer.twitter.com
4-Click ‘Create an app’
5-Fill out the form 
6-Go to the next page, click on the Keys and Access Tokens tab, 
and copy your API key and API secret key. Scroll down and click on Create Access token & access token secret,
and copy your Access token, and Access token secret




1-Install Python
2-pip install tweepy----on powershell
3-Download anaconda for python-optional
4-pip install jupyterlab--for writting the code
5-pip install voila
